{"tid":2111051,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"馬鞍山火燒男子案 控方指當日「可能係香港最黑暗嘅時間」","createTime":"2020-07-16T09:47:33.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-16T14:25:11.000Z","uid":56115,"like":4,"dislike":163,"uniUserReply":69,"replies":[{"pid":"a714677a98da5f71a8be90d05fe36036118412e9","tid":2111051,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-16T09:47:33.000Z","msg":"地盤工去年11月「黎明行動」當天，在馬鞍山追趕涉嫌破壞港鐵站的黑衣人，追至附近天橋時與途人爭執，其間遭淋潑易燃液體及點火，導致全身着火。一對在場夫婦被指當日事前曾向工人爆粗，女方並大叫「返大灣區」，夫婦因而被控在公眾地方作出擾亂秩序行為罪。控方大狀黎安妮今早結案陳詞指，常人看見事主血流披面，理應報警，惟當時「冇人做一個正常市民應該做嘅嘢」，形容案發時社會狀況很差，更謂：「可能係香港最黑暗嘅時間。」案件下月17日裁決。<br />\n<br />\n控方讚揚事主追趕破壞港鐵站的人見義勇為，亦無證據顯示事主曾打人。主控形容，案發時社會狀況非常差，又謂：<span class=\"red\">「法官閣下都可能記得，可能係香港最黑暗嘅時間。」林官聞言表示：「或者呢啲我都唔方便去講。」</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200716/UMYS3DTHPPA7VQZZYCSEMFPMAA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200716%2FUMYS3DTHPPA7VQZZYCSEMFPMAA%2F&d=q%2BUwj3SihaKoadPXZHTFaf5uq9964iqXyfozsjiZLe8%3D&h=d828b75c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200716%2FUMYS3DTHPPA7VQZZYCSEMFPMAA%2F&h=a630d3a1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200716/UMYS3DTHPPA7VQZZYCSEMFPMAA/</a>"},{"pid":"bfd4c525713d065ffcb47cd508b6af43f86af4f8","tid":2111051,"uid":241504,"like":14,"dislike":5,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-16T09:48:49.000Z","msg":"Over my dead body"},{"pid":"c193611a2fe1ebc564e69f913d974affe2d9582f","tid":2111051,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-16T09:49:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"00720671942550a1b29d755f378dad92e24b24c8","tid":2111051,"uid":108016,"like":97,"dislike":1,"score":96,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-07-16T09:49:37.000Z","msg":"好人好者點會無啦啦比人燒"},{"pid":"56d85c2d0763c1addb0343253ed9c0599cd4bd49","tid":2111051,"uid":192776,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"20